648
00:28:32,180 --> 00:28:33,340
Any new findings?

649
00:28:33,340 --> 00:28:34,340
Not so far.

650
00:28:35,460 --> 00:28:36,300
Keep looking.

651
00:28:36,380 --> 00:28:37,380
Thanks for the hard work.

652
00:29:06,060 --> 00:29:06,900
Mom.

653
00:29:08,420 --> 00:29:09,300
Mom.

