670
00:29:47,140 --> 00:29:47,980
Got it.

671
00:29:49,210 --> 00:29:50,260
Everyone, keep checking.

672
00:29:50,260 --> 00:29:51,480
See if there are any other clues.

673
00:29:55,260 --> 00:29:56,580
China Welfare Lottery, right?

674
00:29:56,750 --> 00:29:57,700
Fengyang Police Station.

675
00:29:57,940 --> 00:29:59,900
Help me check
the address of a lottery shop.

676
00:30:02,260 --> 00:30:03,130
Hui.

677
